{"tid":1687122,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"3/11 開始區選冷靜期!","createTime":"2019-11-01T15:12:19.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-01T23:27:04.000Z","uid":316813,"like":3,"dislike":24,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"53423cf5d99a4e545e3f6f9fa4787dc05484326a","tid":1687122,"uid":316813,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T15:12:19.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">各位聼日出來之後可唔可以停兩個禮拜，比個冷靜期，忍到區議會選舉完?</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n好多手足好努力拉緊票，難得無DQ，要打低建制派。如果呢兩個禮拜比政府揾藉口將成個選舉 DQ就唔抵啦<br />\n<br />\n我知好多人會話區議會有叉用，但大家有係咪想建制派繼續每個月領萬萬聲嘅公帑做人工? 呢筆錢去到泛民手上，可以做好多野，例如打司法復核! <br />\n<br />\n呢兩個禮拜唔係叫大家完全放棄，只係希望冷靜下，五好令我們嘅辛勞成為政府嘅藉口。文宣，創意抗爭當然可以繼續<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n大家點睇歡迎討論<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">光復香港 時代革命 聽日見</span></span>"},{"pid":"b9b3ccb919b0ec2ab0fff6e482fdad2afeeb2e55","tid":1687122,"uid":156096,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T15:13:05.000Z","msg":"唔好意思，推post &amp; 借個靚位<br />\n<br />\n******眾籌*******<br />\n鐘庭耀教授為今次運動發起了超大型全港性民調，長期追蹤今次運動大事件的民意 (eg. 721, 831) &amp; 證明香港人未放棄，然後做份國際文宣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />, 話比全世界聽：5毛網軍不代表香港人<br />\n(<span style=\"color: red;\">眾籌到而家先40%</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />, 仲要大家支持)<br />\n<br />\n第二期民調結果POST <span style=\"color: red;\">(new)</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1686054\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1686054</a><br />\n第一期民調結果POST<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1675545\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1675545</a><br />\n<br />\n民調眾籌LINK﹕<a href=\"https://www.collaction.hk/project/story/1209\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.collaction.hk%2Fproject%2Fstory%2F1209&d=rxvDypeE%2FV4%2FTsysNGkz8J1DrXAeA17tgS6Eh9jzous%3D&h=2ec55ba5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.collaction.hk/project/story/1209</a>"},{"pid":"503bee2ee1f0e74be2abbfeb97ada90ed5fb4bdc","tid":1687122,"uid":326665,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T15:14:41.000Z","msg":"唔係冷靜期，係打文宣戰"},{"pid":"d1f3fdef5769459fe74deea287a8b7fb1c798ea6","tid":1687122,"uid":316813,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"503bee2ee1f0e74be2abbfeb97ada90ed5fb4bdc","tid":1687122,"uid":326665,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T15:14:41.000Z","msg":"唔係冷靜期，係打文宣戰"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T15:17:50.000Z","msg":"係 我係呢個意思 想暫時pause前線<br />\n但唔知大家點睇"},{"pid":"e661f78f51da6014d424d5c6cd93b67ad7a184fc","tid":1687122,"uid":263058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T15:18:41.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a5ae4c4124f0c6737cd7243370e02af8873d579a","tid":1687122,"uid":45466,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"53423cf5d99a4e545e3f6f9fa4787dc05484326a","tid":1687122,"uid":316813,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T15:12:19.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">各位聼日出來之後可唔可以停兩個禮拜，比個冷靜期，忍到區議會選舉完?</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n好多手足好努力拉緊票，難得無DQ，要打低建制派。如果呢兩個禮拜比政府揾藉口將成個選舉 DQ就唔抵啦<br />\n<br />\n我知好多人會話區議會有叉用，但大家有係咪想建制派繼續每個月領萬萬聲嘅公帑做人工? 呢筆錢去到泛民手上，可以做好多野，例如打司法復核! <br />\n<br />\n呢兩個禮拜唔係叫大家完全放棄，只係希望冷靜下，五好令我們嘅辛勞成為政府嘅藉口。文宣，創意抗爭當然可以繼續<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n大家點睇歡迎討論<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">光復香港 時代革命 聽日見</span></span>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T23:21:36.000Z","msg":"區議員可以選特首同互選立法會。"},{"pid":"1049ceb56b4700abb167c95a30bd8d50c968da93","tid":1687122,"uid":2676,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T23:24:26.000Z","msg":"收皮啦樓主"},{"pid":"26e4495fe8a72a871ab1011e478e0f067cc6210b","tid":1687122,"uid":34867,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T23:25:40.000Z","msg":"Gphone咩黎，點樣冇DQ?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"70181c0abb8d43d6cda1c60579db14979e006625","tid":1687122,"uid":1241,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T23:25:43.000Z","msg":"收皮啦屌你老母 <br />\n十一月又叫人休息<br />\n冇撚野呀你"},{"pid":"d1e066a4557900b835917c9c9ef97212a0a787fb","tid":1687122,"uid":1241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"26e4495fe8a72a871ab1011e478e0f067cc6210b","tid":1687122,"uid":34867,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T23:25:40.000Z","msg":"Gphone咩黎，點樣冇DQ?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T23:26:34.000Z","msg":"Gphone變咗condom<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c9bfa61ea5d7a1fec4a0019d2422e13cbddd5e20","tid":1687122,"uid":4396,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T23:26:54.000Z","msg":"休息撚重出江湖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n不推文"},{"pid":"c6db13ea194bccdbf3344d4ab95d07026225c0b9","tid":1687122,"uid":197691,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T23:27:04.000Z","msg":"<str